having sent about 4,000 people abroad each year for further
training. Some multinationals spend several million yuan annually
on follow-up training programs, as well.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin is in the forefront in terms of utilization of foreign
funds, which has had steady growth for 4 consecutive years.
</P>
<P>
