Captain, the Minister of Foreign Affairs; Peter Dona Chana, the
Minister of Justice. They all served in Ruth Perry's interim
government.
</P>
<P>
Ellen Spinsman was nominated the Minister of State for
Presidential Affairs.
</P>
<P>
Taylor also named Richard Goodrich as the Secretary to the
Government.
</P>
<P>
