refugees compared with other countries in the world. "In the past
eight years, we have hosted about 4.5 million foreign nationals in
our country."
</P>
<P>
Based on the new plan, the new ID cards will replace the green
and blue cards that the government had given to refugees in Iran,
according to the paper. 
