<HEADLINE> 4th ASEAN Regional Forum Opens in Malaysia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PETAILING JAYA, Malaysia, July 27 (Xinhua) -- The Fourth ASEAN
Regional Forum (ARF) opened here this morning with foreign
ministers or representatives from ASEAN member and observer
countries and dialogue partners attending.
</P>
<P>
