institutions and ensure the timely payment of federal employees'
salary, retirees' pensions and the military's wages and provisions.
</P>
<P>
The deputy prime minister said the energy department, where he
was in charge, had already accomplished the institutional
streamlining work and 25 percent of the staff would be laid off.
</P>
